• we support regulatory initiatives aimed at banning certain 
single-use plastic applications;
• we are rolling out the Operation Clean Sweep certification 
program, which aims to prevent the loss of pellets to the 
environment throughout the plastics value chain;
• we are involved in coalitions such as the Alliance to End 
Plastic Waste, of which we are a founding member and 
which brings together players in the plastics value chain, 
from the production of raw materials to waste collection, 
to work on solutions to eliminate plastic waste in the environment.
